Genre: Animated Action-Comedy 
Cast: Lana Condor, Toni Collette, Annie Murphy, Sam Richardson, Liza Koshy, Will Forte, Colman Domingo and Jane Fonda 
Written by: Pam Brady and Brian C Brown & Elliott DiGuiseppi 
Director:  Kirk DeMicco
Producer: Kelly Cooney Cilella, p.g.a.
Co-Director: Faryn Pearl
Co-Producer: Rachel Zusser
Executive Producer: Mike Mitchell 

Sometimes the hero you are meant to be lies just beneath the surface. 

This summer, DreamWorks Animation dives into the turbulent waters of high school with a hilarious, heartfelt action comedy about a shy teenager who discovers that sheâ€™s part of a legendary royal lineage of mythical sea krakens and that her destiny, in the depths of the oceans, is bigger than she ever dreamed. 

Sweet, awkward 16-year-old Ruby Gillman (Lana Condor, To All the Boys Iâ€™ve Loved Before franchise) is desperate to fit in at Oceanside High, but she mostly just feels invisible. Sheâ€™s math-tutoring her skater-boy crush (Jaboukie Young-White, Ralph Breaks the Internet), who only seems to admire her for her fractals, and sheâ€™s prevented from hanging out with the cool kids at the beach because her over-protective supermum (OscarÂ® nominee Toni Collette, Knives Out), has forbade Ruby from ever getting in the water. 

But when she breaks her mumâ€™s #1 rule, Ruby will discover that she is a direct descendant of the warrior Kraken queens and is destined to inherit the throne from her commanding grandmother (Academy AwardÂ® winner Jane Fonda), the Warrior Queen of the Seven Seas. 

The Kraken are sworn to protect the oceans of the world against the vain, power-hungry mermaids who have been battling with the Kraken for eons. Thereâ€™s one major, and immediate, problem with that: The schoolâ€™s beautiful, popular new girl, Chelsea (Emmy winner Annie Murphy, Schittâ€™s Creek) just happens to be a mermaid. Ruby will ultimately need to embrace who she is and go big to protect those she loves most. 

Ruby Gillman, Teenage Kraken stars an extraordinary cast that includes Emmy winner Colman Domingo (Fear the Walking Dead) as Rubyâ€™s supportive dad, Emmy nominee Sam Richardson (Veep) as Rubyâ€™s enthusiastic uncle and Blue Chapman (Council of Dads) as Rubyâ€™s cool little brother. 

Directed by Academy AwardÂ®-nominated filmmaker Kirk DeMicco (Vivo, The Croods) and produced by Kelly Cooney Cilella, p.g.a. (Trolls World Tour, Trolls), with Faryn Pearl (The Croods: A New Age, Trolls World Tour) serving as co-director, the film features a comedic powerhouse supporting cast, including Emmy nominee Will Forte (The Last Man on Earth), Emmy nominee Nicole Byer (Nailed It!), YouTube Diamond creator Liza Koshy (Liza on Demand), Ramona Young (Never Have I Ever), Eduardo Franco (Stranger Things), Echo Kellum (Arrow), and award-winning social media creator and podcaster Emma Chamberlain (Anything Goes podcast). 

The film is written by Emmy winning South Park producer Pam Brady (Lady Dynamite) and Brian C Brown (Briarpatch) & Elliott DiGuiseppi (Lucy in the Sky). The executive producer is Mike Mitchell (director of next yearâ€™s Kung Fu Panda 4) and the co-producer is Rachel Zusser (associate producer, The Croods: A New Age).

title: Lindt Excellence "Told You So"
TISSOT | Seastar 40mm Quartz
description:
Tissot is delighted to announce a new 40mm edition of the stylish, high-performance Seastar 1000 collection of sports watches. The Seastar 1000 Quartz 40mm sits perfectly between the 36mm and 45.5mm iterations of the Seastar 1000 already available. 

This hugely versatile case size is designed to cater for men and women looking for a chic, yet bold watch that can cross over from day to night while still promising exceptional technical performance. 

As with the existing 36mm and 45.5mm models, the new pieces take their name from their water resistance certification of 1,000 feet, equivalent to 30 ATM or 300 metres. They also offer uni-directional rotating bezels for reliably timing underwater activity. 

Shades of night and day
The new Seastar 1000 Quartz 40mm will be available in three colourways. First is a new but reassuringly ageless combination of black lacquered dial and black mineral bezel with clear, white detailing. Alongside this are models with a blue lacquered dial and blue mineral bezel with white detailing, and an upscale iteration that marries a black lacquered dial and black mineral bezel with golden detailing. The blue and black-and-gold options are also available in the 36mm case size introduced in summer 2022. 

Each colourway has been chosen and refined to offer exceptional clarity and sophistication. Low-light legibility is further enhanced by the application of Super-LumiNovaÂ® to the watchesâ€™ hands and hour markers. 

The theme of refinement continues into the case and integrated three-link stainless steel metal bracelet, which have a blend of brushed and polished finishes to create contrast and texture. The black and gold version comes on a matching black rubber strap. 

Change it up
Throughout the Seastar 1000 Quartz 40mm models, straps and bracelets can be interchanged using Tissotâ€™s easy-to-use quick strap change system, giving the owner the opportunity to choose from a wide range of compatible Tissot straps and personalise their watch to suit mood or occasion. The change can be made by simply clipping out and clipping in â€“ no visits to the jeweller or tool required.

This flexible, high-comfort approach to watch design is a key element in delivering versatility and one of the reasons watch buyers continue to return to Tissot for stylish, day-to-night, go-anywhere watches.

Keeping you on time
The Seastar 1000 Quartz 40mm collection is powered by a high-quality Swiss Made quartz movement that delivers time and date functions with exceptional precision and reliability. And when the time comes to replace the battery, each model is equipped with Tissotâ€™s EOL, or end-of-life indicator. This way, the wearer will know to replace the battery when itâ€™s running low, rather than once itâ€™s fully depleted. No unexpected drops in service.

Can we call it â€œtecheleganceâ€? 
From first glance to everyday use, the Seastar 1000 Quartz 40mm model communicates style, performance and versatility. Each model is a harmonious marriage of elegance and technology, bringing Swiss watchmaking know-how and eternal design together.

title: With HoneyBook, Business Flows Your Way
description:
HoneyBook's complete suite of business management tools help creative entrepreneurs and small business owners work on their own terms.

What is HoneyBook?

HoneyBook is an easy-to-use software platform designed to help small business owners streamline their processes and manage clients from inquiry to payment.

HoneyBookâ€™s goal is to help small business owners sustain a successful business, so they can live out the life they envision for themselves.

How do I get started on HoneyBook?

We offer a free 7-day trial to get you goingâ€”no credit card required! Youâ€™ll have full access to a HoneyBook account, allowing you to play around and make sure itâ€™s right for your business. If you need assistance, you can live chat with our product specialists from right within the platformâ€”or request a demo for an even more hands-on experience!

Once you decide to start your membership, our team can even help you set up your account to make sure you really hit the ground running.

What type of support do you offer?

Once youâ€™re a member, the world is your oyster! Our support team is available 7 days a week via chat and email (Mon-Fri 6am-6pm PT, Sat-Sun 8am-5pm PT), and you can also check out our Help Center 24 hours a day.

For more in-depth training, sign up for one of our many live webinars, which cover everything from the basics of account setup to advanced tools and business management. We host these sessions multiple times a week, so pick the one that suits your schedule!

And donâ€™t forget: we also offer one-time complimentary account setup! Our team can import your business materials in just a few days to make sure you and your business hit the ground running.

What types of small businesses use HoneyBook?

A variety of small businesses have found HoneyBook helpful for booking clients, staying organized, and streamlining their business. Some of our most popular types of users include: graphic designers, djs, photographers, business coaches, web designers, consultants, interior designers, videographers, calligraphers, business coaches, health & wellness professionals, doulas, caterers, event planners, copywriters, bakers, florists, travel professionals and more.

What features does HoneyBook offer?

HoneyBook offers easy-to-use features that help small business owners run their business more efficiently and seamlessly manage clients from first inquiry to final payment. Learn more about our HoneyBook features
Core features include:

- Lead capture (contact form)
- Project management
- Streamlined client communication
- Templates
- Invoices
- Proposals (invoice + contract)
- Contracts
- Brochures
- Questionnaires
- Online payments
- Bookkeeping
- iOS and Android App

Can I import my existing Templates?

Yes! HoneyBook has a number of file, email, and pricing Templates that you can build into your account to save you time down the line. Or, you can take advantage of our one-time, complimentary account building serviceâ€”our team can build your first Templates for you to help get you started! account building service â€”our team can build your first Templates for you to help get you started!

Is HoneyBook a CRM?

HoneyBook is a cloud-based customer relationship management (CRM) built for small businesses. Itâ€™s an easy-to-use software built to help small business owners streamline their business processes from inquiry to invoicing. HoneyBook lets users manage projects, book clients, sign contracts online, send invoices and accept payments.

On HoneyBook users are able to view and track various stages of a project, as well as keep invoices, contracts and other documents in one place. Plus, users can respond to clients quickly and professionally with automated follow-ups using personalized templates and notifications. In addition, automated payment reminders can be sent and task reminders can be created based on the projects.

HoneyBook integrates with tools such as
QuickBooks, Calendly, Zapier, Gmail and Google Calendar

title: Protect your cat from fleas and ticks with Credelio CAT
description:
Protect your cat from fleas and ticks with CredelioÂ® CAT (lotilaner). Nothing should come between you and your best feline friend. Credelio Cat provides long-lasting flea and tick protection in a small, tasty chewable that's easy to give. It's gentle enough even for kittens 8 weeks of age and older, and is approved to treat and prevent fleas in kittens 8 weeks or older weighing 2 pounds or greater and to treat black-legged ticks in kittens 6 months of age or older weighing 2 pounds or greater. Stay close with your cat. Credelio close. Learn more at http://www.credeliocatclose.com

INDICATIONS
Credelio CAT kills adult fleas and is indicated for the treatment and prevention of flea infestations for one month in cats and kittens 8 weeks of age and older and weighing 2 pounds or greater. Credelio CAT is also indicated for treatment and control of black-legged tick infestations for one month in cats and kittens 6 months of age and older and weighing 2 pounds or greater.

IMPORTANT SAFETY INFORMATION
Lotilaner is a member of the isoxazoline class of drugs. This class has been associated with neurologic adverse reactions including tremors, incoordination, and seizures. Neurologic adverse reactions have been reported in cats receiving isoxazoline class drugs, even in cats without a history of neurologic disorders. Use with caution in cats with a history of neurologic disorders. The safety of Credelio CAT has not been established in breeding, pregnant and lactating cats. The effectiveness of Credelio CAT against black-legged ticks in kittens less than 6 months of age has not been evaluated. The most frequently reported adverse reactions are weight loss, rapid breathing and vomiting. For complete safety information, please see Credelio CAT product label or ask your veterinarian.

See full safety information at https://www.elancolabels.com/us/credelio-cat

title: Chop Suey
description:
Young's Chop Suey!! A must delicacy in Iftar

Ingredients for Noodles (For 5 persons)
Spaghetti: Half packet
Salt: As per taste
Water: Boiled 1 liter 
Cooking oil: As required

Preparation for Noodles
Boil water in a pan, add salt and spaghetti, and cook for 5 minutes. When the spaghetti boils, strain it. Heat oil in a pan and fry the spaghetti until golden brown. (The spaghetti will form a bunch)

Ingredients for Young's Mayo Chicken Sauce

Young's Mayonnaise: 1.5 Cup
Chicken fillet: 250gm (Cut thinly into long pieces)
Soy sauce: 2 Tablespoons
Carrot: 1 medium size
Capsicum: 1
Green onion (Chop finely) 1 Tablespoon
Garlic ginger paste: 1 Tablespoon
Red pepper (Powdered) 1 Teaspoon
Tomato: 2
Onion: 1
Green coriander: 1 Tablespoon
Salt: As per taste
Cooking oil: 3 Tablespoons

Preparation for Young's Mayo Chicken Sauce
Add garlic, ginger paste, salt, red pepper, and soy sauce to the chicken fillet and marinate for 15 minutes. Heat oil in a pan and fry the chicken, then add all the vegetables and saute well, then add water and Young's mayonnaise. The delicious Young's Mayo Chicken Sauce is ready

Chop Suey Serving:

Then he washes his big bear fur before he slides into his clean bed sheets

He pats his big bear pillow to make it soft and pretends itâ€™s a cloud
He lowers his big bear voice to be very quiet instead of loud.

He gently crawls into his big bear bed and lays his furry body down.
He makes sure he has a smile on his face instead of a sour frown

He wraps himself in his big bear blanket with his peaceful paws at his side

And then when his ritual is all complete and his big bear worries are gone.
He finally relaxes deeply and lets out his big bear yawn.

Yawwwnnnn.... 

Good night big bear

Good night to the baby bears too

The youngest of King Tritonâ€™s daughters, and the most defiant, Ariel longs to find out more about the world beyond the sea, and while visiting the surface, falls for the dashing Prince Eric. title: TROLLS BAND TOGETHER | Official Trailer
description:
Trolls Band Together - In Theaters November 17

This holiday season, get ready for an action-packed, all-star, rainbow-colored family reunion like no other as Anna Kendrick and Justin Timberlake return for the new chapter in DreamWorks Animationâ€™s blockbuster musical franchise: Trolls Band Together. 

After two films of true friendship and relentless flirting, Poppy (Anna Kendrick) and Branch (Justin Timberlake) are now officially, finally, a couple (#broppy)! As they grow closer, Poppy discovers that Branch has a secret past. He was once part of her favorite boyband phenomenon, BroZone, with his four brothers: Floyd (Golden Globe nominated electropop sensation Troye Sivan), John Dory (Eric AndrÃ©; Sing 2), Spruce (Grammy winner Daveed Diggs; Hamilton) and Clay (Grammy winner Kid Cudi; Donâ€™t Look Up). BroZone disbanded when Branch was still a baby, as did the family, and Branch hasnâ€™t seen his brothers since.  

But when Branchâ€™s bro Floyd is kidnapped for his musical talents by a pair of nefarious pop-star villainsâ€”Velvet (Emmy winner Amy Schumer; Trainwreck) and Veneer (Grammy winner and Tony nominee Andrew Rannells; The Book of Mormon)â€”Branch and Poppy embark on a harrowing and emotional journey to reunite the other brothers and rescue Floyd from a fate even worse than pop-culture obscurity. 

Featuring Trollsâ€™ signature psychedelic joy-bomb of new and classic pop hits, Trolls Band Together stars a dazzling cast of musical superstars and comedic powerhouses as new franchise characters, including four-time Grammy nominee and Latin Grammy winner Camila Cabello (Cinderella) as Viva; Zosia Mamet (The Flight Attendant) as Crimp; and 12-time Emmy winning drag icon RuPaul Charles as Miss Maxine. 

The returning cast includes Grammy, Emmy and Golden Globe nominee Zooey Deschanel as Bridget; Christopher Mintz-Plasse as Gristle, the Icona Pop duo Aino Jawo and Caroline Hjelt as Satin and Chenille, Grammy winner Anderson .Paak as Prince D, comedian Ron Funches as Cooper, SAG nominee Kunal Nayyar as Guy Diamond and Emmy winning Saturday Night Live legend Kenan Thompson as Tiny Diamond. 

Trolls Band Together is steered by returning director Walt Dohrn and producer Gina Shay, and is co-directed by Tim Heitz (head of story, Trolls World Tour). DreamWorks Animationâ€™s Trolls filmsâ€”2016â€™s Trolls and 2020â€™s Trolls World Tourâ€”have sung and danced their way to record-breaking success, earning an OscarÂ® nomination for Best Original Song and fueling one of the largest and most beloved entertainment brands in the world.

This Summer, meet the residents of Element City

Watch the new trailer for Disney and Pixarâ€™s #Elemental and see the movie in 3D, only in theaters June 16!

Check out a brand-new trailer for Disney and Pixarâ€™s â€œElemental,â€ an all-new original feature film that transports moviegoers to an extraordinary place called Element City, where a host of elements live and work. The trailer showcases each elementâ€”air, earth, water and fireâ€”and what sets them apart according to Ember, a quick-witted and fiery woman whoâ€™s always stayed close to home in Firetown. In â€œElemental,â€ which opens in theaters on June 16, she finally ventures out of her comfort zone to explore this spectacular world born from the imaginations of Pixarâ€™s filmmakers and specifically crafted for the big-screen experience. Element City is inspired by big cities around the globe and embraces theorized contributions from each elemental communityâ€”from giant pine-tree-like buildings and waterfall skyscrapers to a tornado-shaped arena called Cyclone Stadium. 

Joining the previously announced voice cast including Leah Lewis and Mamoudou Athie as Ember and Wade, respectively, are Ronnie del Carmen as Emberâ€™s soon-to-be retired dad, Bernie; Shila Ommi as Emberâ€™s love-seeking mom, Cinder; Wendi McLendon-Covey as Wadeâ€™s stormy and Air-Ball-loving boss, Gale; Catherine Oâ€™Hara as Wadeâ€™s welcoming mom, Brook; Mason Wertheimer as Emberâ€™s admiring earth neighbor, Clod; and Joe Pera as an overgrown city bureaucrat, Fern.
 
Directed by Peter Sohn, produced by Denise Ream, p.g.a., and executive produced by Pete Docter, â€œElementalâ€ features a screenplay by John Hoberg & Kat Likkel and Brenda Hsueh with story by Sohn, Hoberg & Likkel and Hsueh. The filmâ€™s original score was composed and conducted by Thomas Newman.

title: oToGuard - The World's First All in one ADAS System for Large Commercial Vehicles
description:
oToGuard is equipped with 1 automotive-grade ECU system, 8 cameras, and vision-Al deep learning technology. The vision-Al algorithm can detect and classify different kinds of vehicles/pedestrian/two-wheeler riders/lane marking and other objects for different purpose.
With 2 front-view cameras, it supports FCW, LDW, MOIS (UN R159) ADAS functions from 0~100 meters without blind spots. With 4 sideview cameras, it supports BSIS (UN R151) to protect vulnerable road users, especially pedestrian and two-wheeler riders within 40 meters without blind spot. With 1 rear view camera, it can support REIS (UN R158) and combine with other cameras mentioned above to support AV/M as well. With 1 in-cabin IR camera, the vision-Al algorithm can recognize over 50 drivers' identification and categorize over 10 kinds of driving status. Furthermore, its less than 20 centimeter high-precision lane detection can operate on straight and curve roads with a radius over 120m which allows the vehicle to enable level 2+ ADAS functions such as ACC, AEB, LCA, LKA, etc.

title: Create Character Animation with Unity HDRP and iClone  - Jasper Hesseling @mastjappa

https://www.reallusion.com/auto-setup/unity/default.html

Experienced 3D artist Jasper Hesseling shares his iClone-to-Unity workflow, using the Auto Setup plugin to seamlessly transfer his CC4-based character, Lynn, to Unity for HDRP rendering with realistic digital human shaders. By leveraging the animation previews in Unity Auto Setup and Reallusion's Parkour motion pack, he creates an impressive action sequence, complete with lifelike facial expressions.

In this video, Jasper guides viewers through each critical step and provides valuable insights into creating his â€œsecret agentâ€. He showcases the versatility of the Character Creator pipeline and also incorporates other powerful 3D tools such as Marvelous Designer, Substance Painter, KitBash3D, Cascadeur, and ZBrush.

description:
Malware - Tipos y cÃ³mo proteger tu PC

Malware es el tÃ©rmino utilizado para identificar programas maliciosos o daÃ±inos para tu PC. El malware es un software que estÃ¡ destinado a daÃ±ar o deshabilitar computadoras y sistemas informÃ¡ticos. Para luchar contra el malware y proteger tu computadora, necesitas usar herramientas como antivirus, anti spywares y firewalls; muchos de los cuales se pueden encontrar de forma gratuita en la web. TambiÃ©n hay suites de seguridad completas disponibles para integrar a tu computadora Dell, lo que facilita enormemente la protecciÃ³n de tu sistema.

Virus
Un virus es un programa de capaz de autorreplicarse. Una vez que una computadora estÃ¡ infectada con un virus, Ã©ste puede propagarse a muchos otros archivos de tu computadora. Los virus se pueden propagar muy fÃ¡cilmente por Internet a travÃ©s de la descargas de archivos.

Worms o Gusanos
Un Worm es un tipo de malware ligeramente diferente. Al igual que los virus, pueden auto-replicarse, pero los gusanos son capaces de enviarse a sÃ­ mismos a muchas personas diferentes. Son muy peligrosos y pueden propagarse automÃ¡ticamente enviando mensajes a las personas de tu lista de contactos.

Troyanos
Un troyano tÃ©cnicamente no es un virus porque normalmente no puede hacer copias de sÃ­ mismo. Algunos troyanos se auto replican, pero generalmente son aplicaciones aparentemente Ãºtiles que has instalado que pueden abrir una puerta trasera secreta desde donde los hackers pueden ingresar y robar tu informaciÃ³n. La mayorÃ­a de las veces no tienes idea de que estÃ¡s infectado con un troyano.

Spyware
El spyware es similar a un troyano, pero en lugar de permitir que un pirata informÃ¡tico acceda a tu PC, lo espÃ­a silenciosamente. El spyware puede robar los nÃºmeros de tu tarjeta de crÃ©dito, informaciÃ³n de tu cuenta bancaria y cualquier otra informaciÃ³n confidencial y personal que tengas en tu computadora. A menudo estÃ¡ incluido con software de procedencia desconocida  para que se instale sin que te des cuenta.

Adware
Adware es bÃ¡sicamente lo mismo que Spyware, aunque no siempre es tan malicioso. Se instala en tu computadora e intenta mostrarte anuncios o publicidad relevante y de forma agresiva. Muchos de estos muestran tantos anuncios que pueden ralentizar su PC.

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'.

title: Chiara Boni White | Milano, SÃ¬ Sposaitalia 2023 Fashion Show
description:
Chiara Boni, famosa designer del marchio ambasciatore del Made in Italy in tutto il mondo, prende parte per la prima volta a una manifestazione di settore: a SÃ¬ Sposaitalia Collezioni, in programma dal 14 al 17 aprile a Milano (Allianz MiCo), presenterÃ  unâ€™anteprima esclusiva della nuova collezione CHIARA BONI White. 

In un contesto raffinato che esalta lâ€™esperienza e la maestria sartoriale dei migliori brand per abiti da sposa, sposo e cerimonia, Chiara Boni trova il suo spazio con il jersey iconico della linea La Petite Robe, creato con cura artigianale per abiti dal taglio armonioso, che accarezzano la silhouette.

Da sempre promotrice di una moda dal segno caratteristico, estremamente femminile e contemporanea, ripropone la stessa allure elegante e impeccabile negli abiti bianchi da sposa, che si legano a una certa atmosfera raffinata, declinata in toni moderni, chic e pratici anche nel giorno piÃ¹ importante. Tailleur lineari con piccoli dettagli luminosi e curati, abiti mini e midi in paillettes iridescenti, abiti lunghi con baschine e inserti floreali o sagomati e sinuosi: la proposta White di Chiara Boni prende ispirazione dalla passione e dallâ€™affetto della stilista fiorentina per il suo giardino di fiori. 

Ricerca e qualitÃ  accomunano la collezione di Chiara Boni e la manifestazione milanese, insieme a creativitÃ , stile italiano e tradizione, con uno sguardo contemporaneo e internazionale. Nella collezione sono i particolari a catturare il centro dellâ€™attenzione: i delicati petali di un fiore, le pieghe inedite, le arricciature strategiche. Lâ€™emozione farÃ  da fil rouge anche con lâ€™esposizione del prezioso Abito Luce, progettato dallâ€™Architetto Alessia Galimberti, che rappresenta un elemento di design distintivo.

title: Kolkata (praaner sohor) [official video] - Samudra feat. Priyanka Roy
description:
Samudra proudly presents the love towards the home city Kolkata..the city of joy. The city of culture, heritage, color, diversity and warmth. This foot tapping number was written by Piyali Majumdar Biswas and Sayantan Neogi, Shuvodip did a fantastic job with the arrangement, Priyanka did an amazing job with vocals along with Sayantan, and final audio, mix and master wrapped up by the incredibly talented Sound engineer Mrityunjoy Das in Crossfade studio. 
Avishek Chakraborty (Ronnie) have done an excellent job with the video, showing all the colors of the city have to offer. Three amazing dancers Rhea, Sudeshna and Meany presented three different dance forms which represented three different dimensions of the city. Anik, Sayantan and everyone of the team have done a tremendous job for this amazing little music video. 
Samudra thanks all the people associated with the production, the families and everyone out there who made this possible. Please watch the video, like, share and subscribe to the channel. Please support original music and spread love.
Hope you guys will enjoy this..cheers ğŸ˜ƒ

DIRECTOR'S NOTES

Guru$$ started out as a joke. So many folks in Kundalini yoga had been given a name by Yogi Bhajan..."Gurmukh", "Sopurkh", "Sada Sat Kaur".

People asked my name. I said, "My name is Sada Sat BING" and got a laugh.

It became, "My name is Sada Sat BING, yoga's my thing."

So my new age satire life began, as I did spiritual comedy.

And then I saw what was happening in the yoga community. People think they will get the answers from one person and so they give away their power. Eventually, people, especially women, were exploited.  Not just Western Yoga.  Everywhere.

So I wrote a yoga comedy.

My little rhyme became a rap song.  Hip-hop yoga.  Comedy music about exploitation and ego, with a guru spitting old-school hip-hop. So many musical inspirations, from Slick Rick & Doug E. Fresh to Digable Planets.

Two years and three musicians later, Carl Burnett nailed it on the first pass.

We shot in 2017, again in 2018, and a little bit at the end in 2021 until we were satisfied that the story was clear. It was a lot of work but profoundly fulfilling.

Guru$$ is about a woman who tries to take a shortcut to enlightenment, gets caught up in the glitz, and ends up with nothing.

So yes, it is a comedy...

...and it is also a cautionary tale.

Since we started shooting, documentaries have been released about Bikram and Osho on Netflix, there an entire series on Vice about Yogi Bhajan and other yoga leaders who have exploited others, and last month, there was a Rolling Stone article about another one, Bentinho.

I hope you enjoy our labor of loveâ€¦and maybe get the chorus stuck in your head.

title: Beparwah (Official Video) | Sidhant Kapoor X Ruskin Bond X The Sunshine Orchestra
description:
Sidhant Kapoor, a music composer, was so moved by a poetry called â€˜Slum Children at Playâ€™ by Ruskin Bond, that he drove up the hills of Mussoorie to meet the legendary writer and seek permission to put his words to music. On returning to Mumbai, Sidhant took notice of three street children and realised that they personify the emotions of the poetry. With this inspiration, Sidhant began his journey of composing his first ever single! He brought The Sunshine Orchestra, legendary composer A.R. Rahman's dream project, on board to perform the strings section. He wrote additional lyrics in Hindi and started painting the first few strokes of this composition. All through this process, he was inspired by the story of the three kids that taught him the true meaning of â€˜Beparwahâ€™!

description:
#ExtemporeMusicalJourney #podcast #guitarist 

â–ºPodcast With Paras Ft.Vinod Katoch (Full Episode)

Welcome to Extempore Musical Journeys! I'm excited to introduce you to this unique and exciting project created in collaboration with Two for Joy Studio. Extempore Musical Journeys takes you on a musical voyage like no other, where the destination and musical style are unknown, and the journey is completely improvised. Each episode features talented musicians who come together to create something truly special in the moment. This project is all about pushing boundaries and exploring the unknown, and we can't wait for you to come along for the ride. Get ready for an unforgettable musical experience that will leave you wanting more.
A Pantellisense Production!

â–ºPodcast With Paras Ft.Vinod Katoch (Full Episode)

Episode 3 of Extempore Musical Journeys with Paras and Vinod takes us on a journey to discover finger style guitar. Paras starts off by explaining the basics of finger style guitar and demonstrates a few techniques.

Vinod then picks up his guitar and they start playing Mohit Chauhan's popular song 'Boondein' in finger style. The music is soothing and mesmerizing as their fingers move effortlessly on the strings, producing beautiful melodies.

As they continue playing, Paras and Vinod share their experiences with finger style guitar and how it has opened up new musical avenues for them. They also discuss the importance of practice and perseverance in mastering the technique.

The episode ends with a soulful rendition of 'Boondein' in finger style, leaving the viewers mesmerized and wanting more of such melodious and informative musical journeys.

title: Only a Dream (from the film "Five Moments") - Ted Ganger
description:
This performance is taken from the award-winning short film "Five Moments," soon to be released in its entirety here on YouTube.

Lyrics and music by Ted Ganger
Magdalena Herfurtner (Madil Hardis), voice
(https://www.youtube.com/c/MadilHardis)
Ted Ganger, piano

#MagdalenaHerfurtner #MadilHardis
#TedGanger

You might also like this song sung (and played) as a "Song of the Week" by Ted Ganger.
https://youtu.be/XP3AvWA6boo

ONLY A DREAM

I dreamed that I lay beside her,                                                                                                                   And we were as we used to be.                                                                                                                    But somehow I couldn't believe it,                                                                                                                 And struggled and tried to get free. 
I cried out: I know I'm dreaming.                                                                                                                 She laughed and kept pulling me in.                                                                                                                I fought my way up to the surface                                                                                                                 And woke, full of what had not been.
 
For that couldn't really happen,                                                                                                                     No matter how things might seem,                                                                                                              So go back to sleep, yes, go back to sleep, just go back to sleep -                                                           It was only a dream.

I dreamed she was going to leave me,                                                                                                        She told me I wasn't the one.                                                                                                                       She smoked on a bench in the moonlight                                                                                                  And spoke what she'd already done.
She thought I should hear it directly,                                                                                                          And now she'd get on with her life.                                                                                                                 I'm still sitting there in the moonlight                                                                                                            And still feel the twist of the knife.

But that never really happened,                                                                                                                      No matter how things might seem,                                                                                                                                  So go back to sleep, yes, go back to sleep, just go back to sleep -                                                                                                It was only a dream.


I dreamed that we once were strangers,                                                                                                          Two souls that had gone astray.                                                                                                                                         We both led the life of the lonely,                                                                                                                                                             And both came from far away.
We knew it would not be easy,                                                                                                                       But felt it was destined to be.                                                                                                                                         So I sent my heart on its journey,                                                                                                                                                 And she shared her secrets with me.

It may be that never happened,                                                                                                                      No matter how things might seem,                                                                                                                                  But go back to sleep, yes, go back to sleep, just go back to sleep -                                                                                            Though it's only a dream.

title: Supply Chain Transformed - Future-Proof Supply Chains S2 Ep3 | Digi-Key Electronics
description:
In season 2 of Supply Chain Transformed, we look at how the world is tackling new and ever-present challenges in global logistics. Recent years have shown how much risk truly exists between point A and B, and in this season, weâ€™ll explore how technology is poised to provide visibility and insight into where risk lies, and how to ensure nothing catches us off-guard again.

Billions of dollars are being invested into semiconductor production to combat component shortages. In this episode, we explore the steps needed to ensure that future supply chains are ready and able to meet unexpected surges in demand.

title: Architect-Artist Innovates CG Film Production with CC AccuRIG, Redshift SSS and iClone
description:
https://www.reallusion.com/character-creator/auto-rig.html London-based architect Kay John Yim has set his sights on his next ambitious animation project, "Masquerade," following the completion of his previous works "Ballerina" and "Kagura." Yim is sparing no effort in creating this new debut short CG film and takes us through his character creation workflow in an in-depth video. He demonstrates how he streamlined the process by integrating the auto-rig features in Character Creator 4 (CC) and working with CC AccuRIG, Cinema 4D, and Redshift Random Walk SSS.

Yim's use of the cutting-edge Redshift software (version 3.4.06) paired with the streamlined CC-iClone character workflow synergistically optimizes the creation of stunning, realistic SSS (subsurface scattering) effects, minimizing the time required for rendering and lighting adjustments.

The mesmerizing vanishing effect of the star's cloak is created using Yim's advanced Cinema 4D setup, ultimately revealing her identity and opulent ball gown. His signature style of infusing each character with captivating charm and infusing glamorous sets with cinematic effects shines through in "Masquerade."

Additionally, Yim's utilization of the Edit Motion Layer feature, available exclusively in iCone 8, seamlessly blends motion data from Actocore and Xsens, resulting in his distinct and genuine animation style. In an age where text-to-image AI is ascending, Yim's work serves as a testament to human creativity, honoring the pursuit of art and provoking contemplation on its very essence.

"Masquerade" was featured in the 2023 Cinema 4D and Redshift showreel.
Access the article now for more Pro Tips and CGI resources from Kay John Yim. https://magazine.reallusion.com/2023/05/02/architect-artist-innovates-cg-film-production-with-cc-accurig-redshift-sss-and-iclone/

title: Lead Generation for Private Jet Industry & Understanding Customer Qualification
description:
Private/charter jets industry is a niche market that caters to a high-end clientele seeking luxury travel experiences. Understanding this industry can help in lead generation and customer qualification. Here are some key aspects to consider:

1. Target market: Private/charter jets are primarily used by high-net-worth individuals, corporate executives, celebrities, and government officials. Therefore, understanding the demographics and psychographics of this target market can help in lead generation and customer qualification.

2. Services and amenities: Private/charter jets offer a range of services and amenities such as personalized in-flight catering, luxury interiors, and advanced entertainment systems. Understanding the specific needs and preferences of the target market can help in tailoring the services and amenities to attract and retain customers.

3. Price and value: Private/charter jets are expensive, and pricing varies based on the type of aircraft, distance, and duration of the flight. Understanding the value proposition of the service and communicating it effectively to potential customers can help in generating leads and qualifying customers.

4. Reputation and referrals: Reputation and referrals play a crucial role in the private/charter jets industry. Positive reviews and referrals from satisfied customers can help in generating new leads and qualifying potential customers.

5. Industry regulations: The private/charter jets industry is highly regulated, and compliance with regulations is critical for lead generation and customer qualification. Understanding and complying with industry regulations can help build trust and credibility with potential customers.

6. Compliance: The private/charter jets industry is highly regulated, and it's important to comply with regulations when advertising on Facebook and Google. Be transparent about pricing, disclose any fees or surcharges, and avoid making misleading claims.

title: Shopify Pricing | What is Shopify? | Shopify Website | E-commerce | Shopify Tutorial
description:
Shopify Pricing | What is Shopify? | Shopify Website | E-commerce | Shopify Tutorial

https://profiletree.com/ecommerce-web-design-agency/

Welcome to this ProfileTree video
In this video, we will explain what Shopify pricing plans are available for you to choose from and how you can build and use a website using the eCommerce platform for your own business.

Shopify is an e-commerce platform that allows individuals and businesses to create their own online stores and sell products or services online. It was founded in 2004 and has since grown to become one of the most popular e-commerce platforms in the world. 

Shopify offers several pricing plans that cater to businesses of different sizes and needs. Here are the different Shopify pricing plans and their benefits:

Basic Shopify - $29 per month: This plan is designed for small businesses just starting out with an online store. It includes all the essential features needed to launch a basic online store, including unlimited products, 24/7 customer support, and the ability to accept credit card payments.

Shopify - $79 per month: This plan includes all the features of Basic Shopify, plus more advanced features such as gift cards, professional reports, and the ability to create discount codes. It's a good option for growing businesses with higher sales volumes.

Advanced Shopify - $299 per month: This plan includes all the features of Shopify, plus more advanced features such as advanced report building, third-party calculated shipping rates, and the ability to customize your checkout process. It's ideal for large businesses with high sales volumes and complex needs.

Shopify Plus - Custom pricing: This is the most advanced plan offered by Shopify, designed for enterprise-level businesses with complex needs. It includes all the features of Advanced Shopify, plus personalized support, advanced security features, and custom integrations.

The benefits of Shopify pricing plans include:

Scalability: As your business grows and your needs change, you can upgrade your Shopify plan to access more features and support.

Flexibility: Shopify pricing plans offer flexibility to businesses of different sizes and budgets, with plans designed for small, medium, and large businesses.

Ease of use: Shopify is easy to set up and use, with an intuitive interface and a wide range of apps and integrations available to extend the platform's functionality.

Reliability: Shopify offers reliable hosting, security, and uptime, ensuring that your online store is always available to customers.

Support: Shopify offers 24/7 customer support via phone, email, and live chat, as well as a comprehensive knowledge base and community forums.

Overall, Shopify pricing plans offer a wide range of features and support to help businesses of all sizes launch and grow their online stores.

By the end of this talk, you will understand how a preoccupation with â€œsurvivingâ€ sabotages our chances of â€œthrivingâ€ in our personal life and in our professional life.

Chris has enjoyed high highs and endured low lows.  Now he shares what he learned the hard way, helping seemingly happy and successful people escape the traps they set for themselves so they can find peace, laughter, and fulfillment. The author of seventeen books and board member for a business school and medical school, Chris loves to teach.  He offers keynote speeches, strategy and innovation sessions, executive and team retreats, and â€œgiraffe sellingâ€œ training program. title: Manali Tour | Part-3 | Atal Tunnel | Highest Tunnel in the World | Manali to Lahaul | Lahaul in May
description:
Lahaul district is connected to Manali through the Rohtang Pass. Lahaul Valley of Himachal Pradesh in the northern part of the country has become the most popular tourist destination of Himachal due to its easy approach after the opening of the Atal Tunnel, Rohtang. Lahaul valley is just 33 km from Manali along the Manali-Leh highway. The valley starts from the northern end of the Atal tunnel. The atal tunnel is the bridge between Manali and Lahaul. Before the tunnel, Lahaul was reachable via Rohtang pass. Rohtang top, 51 km from Manali, is the boundary of Manali and Lahaul valley.
Atal Tunnel (also known as Rohtang Tunnel), named after former Prime Minister of India, Atal Bihari Vajpayee is a highway tunnel built under the Rohtang Pass. At a length of 9.02 km, it is the highest highway single-tube tunnel above 10,000 feet (3,048 m) in the world. The tunnel reduces the travel time and overall distance between Manali and Keylong on the way to Leh. The route, which previously went through Gramphu, was 116 km (72.1 mi) long and took 5 to 6 hours in good conditions. Prime Minister Narendra Modi inaugurated the Atal Tunnel in Manali, Himachal Pradesh on 3 October 2020.

title: The benefits of writing by hand | Katie McCleary | TEDxEustis
description: Leadership professor and writing and consciousness expert, Katie McCleary, MFA, offers the benefits of writing by hand for all ages. Based on more than 25 years of writing with thousands of people, McCleary offers insights into the science of handwriting and how it can easily improve your focus, elevate your thinking, deliver the â€œsticky factorâ€ to retain new learning, and create more meaningful, resonate connections. So, go ahead, let go of the grammar police, write in your messy unique font, and see what bubbles up when you try slow and write by hand. Katie McCleary is an author, changemaker, professor of leadership and a lover of people. Earning her MFA, in Writing and Consciousness, led to her belief that handwriting is a path to transform the self, communities and the world. She is also the coauthor of Bridge the Gap, which Inc. named 1 of 3 business books to read in 2022. As the founder of the nonprofit, 916 Ink, Katie has helped more than 4500 young people become confident authors who know the power of the pen. Mashable.com named her 1 of 15 â€œReal Miss Americasâ€ for her career in uplifting communities. She is the host of NPR CapRadioâ€™s leadership podcast, â€œThe Drive.â€ Katie teaches in the Masters of Nonprofit Leadership at Pacific University. Her work has appeared in Forbes, PBS, Shondaland, Thrive, Apple News, and Hip Mama. She lives with 2 children, 15 chickens, 1 talkative parrot, and other furry creatures in California. She is handwriting her next book: A Biomythography of Our Being: What We Become when We Write. This talk was given at a TEDx event using the TED conference format but independently organized by a local community. Learn more at https://www.ted.com/tedx

Childhood friends Hinata and Hayato are training hard in kendo for their final high school inter-high school competition.
One day, Hinata is scouted by an entertainment agency. This causes a rift in their relationship.
The film depicts these two young boys who grow up to be adults while still carrying the pain & doubts from their youth.     

In 2022, the Japan Expo project was inaugurated to draw on the essence of cultures and tales that lie dormant in various areas of Japan and condense them into short stories. Short stories set in Iwate, Shizuoka & Fukuoka Prefectures were submitted & selected. 
At the SSFF & ASIA 2022 Fall Festival held in October 2022, a panel discussion was held with the invited writers of the stories. In addition, the short story "The Two of Us, in a Town with a View of the Sea" by Kento Norikane which was inspired by the novel "Konjiki Yasha" by writer Ozaki KÅyÅ, a famed author whose statue is in Atami City, has been adapted into a short film written & directed by Karin Miyagi and will be distributed worldwide through online screenings.

description:
Welcome to the most star-spangled showdown in the Armageddon Championship Series: Asia & Oceania featuring Vladimir Kramnik, Gukesh D, Yangyi Yu, Nodirbek Abdusattorov, Daniil Dubov, Vidit Gujrathi, Karthikeyan Murali, and Parham Maghsoodloo.

Tune in live on April 7 at 20:00 CET for chess heroes under intense time pressure with a real-time heartbeat and calorie-burned level as they race across the board for the chance to win â‚¬50,000 and two spots in Grand Finale. 

Commentators GM Jan Gustafsson and IM Jovanka Houska will do their best to keep up.

Armageddon Championship Series is a season of ultra-fast blitz tournaments with continental qualifiers and a Grand Finale event. The Series consists of seven-day double-elimination tournaments (if a player loses a match, he or she can still win the tournament and is eliminated after a second loss). Matches consist of two blitz games (3 minutes plus a 2-second move increment) and, if necessary, an Armageddon (5 minutes for White, 4 minutes for Black). There are two matches per day. The top two players of each event secure two places in the Grand Finale. All games are broadcast live from the Armageddon Studio in Berlin, and the total event prize fund of the Series is â‚¬460 000. The Series is organized by World Chess.
